body:
Skills, Knowledge & Expertise:

- Good knowledge in PHP/MySQL;
- Good knowledge with CSS3, Javascript (jQuery);
- Good (speaking and writing) in English;

Nice to have skills:

- Experience with Laravel framework;
- Experience with Oracle & MSSQL;
- Knowledge of Adobe Photoshop or Illustrator;

Main Responsibilities:

- Maintain & develop new features for our existing front-end/backend web platforms in PHP, MySQL, Javascript;
- Work closely with other members of the team to deliver high quality developments;
- Contribute to improving the quality and design of the existing code base;
- Provide technical problem resolution for small problems without assistance;

Offer:

- Competitive salary and other benefits;
- Young and dynamic environment;
- Carrier development opportunities;


If your CV matches the above-described profile, we will contact you in a short time.
For further details about our company and career opportunities please contact us at  hr@betcafearena.ro

Send us your application now!

About us:

Bet Cafe Arena is a Romanian company organizing gambling which offers its clients a new concept of betting agency, designed as an entertainment center.
Our agency customers can bet on sporting events most varied or play electronic slot-machines, while enjoying quality service type events in most agencies.
